## Troubleshooting

| Symptom | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Alert in Wazuh, nothing in n8n | Check `/var/ossec/logs/integrations.log` |
| Script not triggering | `chmod 750` + `chown root:wazuh` on `custom-n8n` |
| VirusTotal 404 | File not in VT database — expected for unknown files |
| ntfy not arriving | Topic name must match exactly in n8n and ntfy app |
| WSL IP changed | Run `hostname -I`, update `ossec.conf`, restart manager |

